summary:
The $SUPRA Public Sale - The $SUPRA Public Sale is scheduled for Wed Oct 25, 2023 at 3PM SGT.

 Supra closes early stage fundraising - Supra has closed its early stage fundraising with over $24M from top VCs.

 Supra research team - Get to know the Supra research team.

 SupraOracles is now - SupraOracles has updated its name to reflect its focus.

 Supra oracle data feeds - Supra's oracle data feeds are live on 40+ networks.

 Supra VRF - Supra VRF allows for the building of dApps with impossible-to-manipulate VRFs.

 IntraLayer - IntraLayer enables the building of cross-chain enabled protocols.

 Supra Network Activate Program - The Supra Network Activate Program offers discounted services and technical support to embed oracles and VRFs.
